<A>__{theo snakes his way along the rows of pin machines, towards the only light source lane six. as he leans in to peer through the machine, a ball explodes into the pins. junior, wearing his elaborate bowling claw, is working himself into a sweaty froth. junior picks up his ball and sends it crashing into the pins.}
