<D>__{what did your dad tell you to do to buzz? theo scrambles up the lane on hands and knees. junior catches him, grabbing his ankles.}
<C>__{junior}
<D>__{he told me to play blue face with buzz. i like games.}
<C>__{theo}
<P>__{(struggling to get away)}
<D>__{what did you do to buzz?}
